Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: rateflix-server
Architecture: amd64
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, curl, gzip, ca-certificates
Description: IMDB rating lookup server
 HTTP service for fuzzy movie/title lookup against local IMDB data files.
 Provides a REST endpoint that accepts title queries and returns IMDB
 ratings using an in-memory inverted index with IDF-weighted scoring.
